import { Flex, Box, Text, Center, Heading } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import '@fontsource/charmonman/'
import '@fontsource/clicker-script'
import '@fontsource/edu-nsw-act-foundation/400.css'
import '../theme'

const head = {
  fontSize: 56,
  fontWeight: 700,
  textAlign: 'left' as const,
  letterSpacing: '2px',
  color: 'space_cadet',
  pl: '2%',
  verticalAlign: 'center' as const
}

const center = {
  fontSize: 32,
  fontWeight: 200,
  textAlign: 'center' as const,
  color: 'ultra_violet',
  w: '33%',
  h: '73px'
}

export default function Header() {
  return (
    <Flex align={'center'}>
      <Box w='50%' h='100%'>
        <Text {...head} >
          Ari Wisenburn
        </Text>
      </Box>
      <Box flex='1' h='73px' pr='2%'>
        <Flex>
          <Center {...center}>
            Projects
          </Center>
          <Center {...center}>
            Contact
          </Center>
          <Center {...center}>
            Download Resume
          </Center>
        </Flex>
      </Box>
    </Flex >
  )
}
